< EXTRA FEATURES:

START_MENU - A welcome screen for the game

CREDITS - credits for the creators

END_GAME_SCREEN - an end screen that shows the user his score and the word he found, and gives him the option to play again

GIF_IMPLEMENTATION: We have gifs in our GUI.

>

Hello there (Real star wars fan knows)


Here some documentation about our boggle game

boggle_board.py:

this file is used to create the board objects for the game.

boggle_controller:

this file links between our game logic to the gui elements.

boggle_gui.py:

this file contains the gui elements for our game.

ImageTk:

a PIL moudle that is imported in case it cant be imported from PIL

resources:

a directory containing the game images and gifs for the gui.
 


